This paper deals with a fingerprinting game, which involves information theory and cryptography (cs.IT and cs.CR). The game also involves multimedia content (cs.MM) and data structures (cs.DS) for embedding fingerprints into a host sequence. Finally, the paper discusses the optimal solution to the game, which involves game theory and optimization (cs.LG).
